nars.nal.nal8

Class Operator<T extends Term>

  • java.lang.Object
    • nars.term.atom.Atomic
      • nars.term.atom.AbstractStringAtomRaw
        • nars.term.atom.AbstractStringAtom
          • nars.nal.nal8.Operator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable, Term, Termed, Termlike

    public final class Operator<T extends Term>
extends AbstractStringAtom
    the 1-arity '^' compound which wraps a term to indicate an operator that can be used as the predicate of an Operation, ex: <(arg0, arg1) --> ^operator> This class also includes static utility methods for working with Operation terms (which include an "Operator", as shown above, but is not an "Operator").
